Eu desafio você.

131
00:18:13,834 --> 00:18:16,667
<i>Glória, glória, aleluia</i>

132
00:18:17,417 --> 00:18:18,709
<i>Espere!</i>

133
00:18:20,209 --> 00:18:21,250
<i>Peguem!</i>

134
00:18:28,000 --> 00:18:29,042
Não se mexa!

135
00:18:32,709 --> 00:18:36,000
